Name: Dinosaur Hunting Patrol 3D Multiplayer Online
About the game: Hunting dinosaurs it’s a multiplayer online game whose target is to protect primates (our ancestors) of dangerous dinosaurs who walk from one place to another in Jurassic, Cretaceous and Triassic era. You have to keep alive primate who will be attacked for dangerous dinosaurs (T-Rex, Spinosaurus, Raptor, Triceratops, Brachiosaurus, Pteranodon, Stegosaurus, Dimetrodon, Paradophosaurus, …). You need another online cooperative player to help you to get the target. Points are shared for both. You will have many weapons, ammi and bullets to use for preserving primates alive. And you will have to keep you alive alone yourself. It’s a realistic game in 3D with free moving ad stereo sound. You will have missions with different difficult levels. And two differents worlds: last day and tropical forest. You will feel danger and feel responsibility for your life and that of others at all times. You can speak with your friends while you play this game.
